flowchart LR
    %% User Flow with Colored Nodes + UC Mapping

    %% Style definitions
    classDef list fill:#D0E8FF,stroke:#1E88E5,color:#000
    classDef create fill:#DFFFD6,stroke:#43A047,color:#000
    classDef detail fill:#FFF7CC,stroke:#FDD835,color:#000
    classDef edit fill:#FFE0E0,stroke:#E53935,color:#000
    classDef board fill:#E8D9FF,stroke:#8E24AA,color:#000
    classDef user fill:#E0E0E0,stroke:#616161,color:#000

    %% Nodes
    U[User]:::user

    L[Tickets List<br/>UC-005/006/007]:::list
    C[Create Ticket<br/>UC-001]:::create
    D[Ticket Detail<br/>UC-002/004]:::detail
    E[Edit Ticket<br/>UC-003]:::edit
    B[Kanban Board<br/>Optional]:::board

    %% Entry
    U --> L

    %% From List
    L -->|Create new ticket| C
    L -->|View ticket| D
    L -->|Board view| B

    %% From Create
    C -->|Submit| D
    C -->|Cancel| L

    %% From Detail
    D -->|Edit info| E
    D -->|Change status| D
    D -->|Back| L
    D -->|Board view| B

    %% From Edit
    E -->|Save| D
    E -->|Cancel| D

    %% From Board
    B -->|Open ticket| D
    B -->|Back to list| L
